if (typeof msg.params.BASE_DEVICE_ID === 'undefined' ||
        typeof msg.params.ZONE === 'undefined' ||
        typeof msg.params.CHANNEL_ID === 'undefined' ||
        typeof msg.params.EVENT_ID === 'undefined' ||
        typeof msg.params.INIT_VALUE === 'undefined' ||
        typeof msg.params.VALUE_TO_STATE === 'undefined') {
    node.error('illegal msg.params')
    return
}

flow.set(
    [
        'BASE_DEVICE_ID',
        'ZONE',
        'CHANNEL_ID',
        'EVENT_ID',
        'INIT_VALUE',
        'VALUE_TO_STATE'
    ],
    [
        msg.params.BASE_DEVICE_ID,
        msg.params.ZONE,
        msg.params.CHANNEL_ID,
        msg.params.EVENT_ID,
        msg.params.INIT_VALUE,
        msg.params.VALUE_TO_STATE
    ]
)

delete msg.params

return msg;

const begin_time = msg.args.utilization_begin_time
const end_time = msg.args.utilization_end_time

const device_id = env.get("device_id")
const channel_id = env.get("channel_id")

msg.query = `
    SELECT "${channel_id}"
    FROM "${device_id}"
    WHERE time >= '${begin_time.toISOString()}'
    AND time < '${end_time.toISOString()}'
`

node.log(msg.query)

return msg;

name: query previous state
func:
const begin_time = msg.args.utilization_begin_time

const device_id = env.get("device_id")
const channel_id = env.get("channel_id")

msg.query = `
    SELECT "${channel_id}"
    FROM "${device_id}"
    WHERE time < '${begin_time.toISOString()}'
    ORDER BY time DESC
    LIMIT 1
`

node.log(msg.query)

return msg;
